# Normalize line endings so Windows/OneDrive checkouts don't show every
# text file as "modified" with no real content change. Git stores LF in
# the repo and converts to the platform's native line ending on checkout.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — never touch these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
